				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Bard Twink Guide<a name="75860"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 26 05 8:20 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Howdy,
<br />

<br />
I'm looking to start up a bard as a possible second main character in the near future.  I will have probably 50-75k, plus a fungi to twink him(probably to be sold at higher levels).  Assume he will be into the 50s shortly, so some req. lvl gear is not out of order.  Is there an all-encompassing guilde on the site somewhere?  I didn't see one with the searches I did, or when I looked through the last few months of posts.  Something along these lines is what I'm looking for: http://www.thesteelwarrior.org/forum/showthread.php?t=9876  
<br />

<br />
I have a couple more questions - I will be choosing human or half-elf.  RZ or Tribunal - not only for the gear.  My current main (Ogre BL) is RZ, and I also like the style of the Tribunal.  Would I be able to do the OT Hammer quest with Tribunal faction?  (assuming not easily)  What would be my starting town for these characters (for origin, and hunting purposes).
<br />

<br />
What instruments are the best combo for soloing up to the 50s?  (assume self-pincushion until no longer practical, charm/fear/swarm after that).  When do I need to look at FT items, and what's a good amount to have by 60ish?  Are the effects on Ornate armor really worth it?  What quests do I need to look at?
<br />

<br />
Thanks for any time you are willing to dedicate to helping me.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
