				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Would I be able to do the OT Hammer quest with Tribunal faction? </span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
I'm sure somebody can correct me if I'm wrong (foggy memory since it's been so long ago when I did it myself), but I think the OT Hammer quest is based upon <b>charming</b> the skelly foreman.  I don't think your starting faction will have any bearing at all on your success.  Once charmed, he will like you.
<br />

<br />
The thing about the skelly foreman, though, is that charm breaks very <b>quickly</b>.  You have to be very fast with your turn-in to him.  At least I seem to remember that being the case when I did it ages ago.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
