				<td colspan="2"><span>magnetic equipment is nice, esp charged magnetic, but i won't list all them in each list but keep that in mind.  also, for people on a budget - keep in mind the 'acrylia plate' equipment.  pretty good AC and with a small hp boost.
<br />

<br />
you may find diety armor also.  like fierce heraldic (RZ) or helanic tundra (tribunal) viable also.
<br />

<br />

<br />
