<br />

<br />

<br />
<u>Finger + Ear</u>
<br />
pick up something with good hp/ac at early levels.  most good rings/ears are REQ 46 or rec 55.
<br />
- velium fire wedding rings  (or the new velium one, AC 8 and +80 hp? - can't think of it's name)
<br />
- Djarn's Amethyst Ring
<br />
- Shadel Bandit Ring
<br />

<br />
should be easy slots to fill.
<br />

<br />

<br />
my advice, choose haste item first, then ignore that slot when purchasing gear.  
<br />

<br />
do searches at eqcardplace.com/eq or http://everquest.allakhazam.com.  for mid 40's gear, be sure to take a look at drops in the newer expansions and the revamped zones.  i.e. lavastorm (sooty miner's cloak(?) and lucky miner's gorget).  also OoW drops in Dranik's, LDoN drops, etc.
<br />

<br />
the newer gear tends to have resist bonuses on them than previous droppable items.
<br />

<br />
this is all i have time for now.
